title: BRIEF-Alexander & Baldwin Qtrly Earnings Per Share $3.42
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - Alexander & Baldwin Inc:
* ALEXANDER & BALDWIN, INC. REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL-YEAR 2017 RESULTS
* Q4 BASIC EARNINGS PER SHARE $4.31 FROM CONTINUING OPERATIONS
* SAME STORE CASH NOI INCREASED 5.5% IN Q4 2017, AS COMPARED TO PRIOR YEAR Q4
* OCCUPANCY INCREASED BY 140 BASIS POINTS TO 93.6% AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2017, AS COMPARED TO PRIOR YEAR-END
* BACKLOG FOR COâ€˜S MATERIALS & CONSTRUCTION SEGMENT WAS $202.1 MILLION AS OF DEC 31, 2017, VERSUS $242.9 MILLION FOR PRIOR YEAR
* QTRLY TOTAL REVENUE $122.7 MILLION VERSUS $111.2 MILLION * QTRLY EARNINGS PER SHARE $3.42 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
